<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.4.10">
<l>poṉṉalarum puṉṉaicūḻ pullāṇi yammāṉai</l>
<l>miṉṉiṭaiyār vēṭkainōy kūra viruntataṉai</l>
<l>kaṉṉavilun tiṇṭōḷ kaliya ṉolivallār</l>
<l>maṉṉavarāy maṇṇāṇṭu vāṉāṭu muṉṉuvarē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who master the words of Kaliyaṉ with strong arms</l>
<l rend="indent">that suggest boulders,</l>
<l>About the lightning-waisted one’s pangs of desire being severe,</l>
<l>About the lord of Pullāṇi, surrounded by laurel trees where gold blossoms,</l>
<l>Having ruled the earth as kings, they will ascend to the heavenly land.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
